## Core Features ‚ö°

### Exam Experience
- **Timer**: 12-minute countdown with warning at 2 minutes
- **Questions**: 10 random questions per exam from 300-question bank
- **Navigation**: Previous/Next buttons, progress bar, question counter
- **Selection**: Checkbox-based multiple selection (can choose 1-3 answers)
- **Auto-submit**: Automatic submission when time expires

### Results & Review
- **Instant Results**: Animated score circle, pass/fail (70% threshold)
- **Detailed Breakdown**: Correct/incorrect count, time taken
- **Review Mode**: See all questions with explanations
- **Visual Feedback**: Green for correct, red for incorrect answers

### Technical Architecture
- **Frontend**: HTML5, CSS3, vanilla JavaScript (no frameworks)
- **Questions**: JSON files (separate per certification)
- **Deployment**: Netlify with automatic CD from GitHub
- **Testing**: Unit tests (Jest) + E2E tests (Playwright)
- **CI/CD**: GitHub Actions for automated testing

